http://doc.rust-lang.org/book/testing.html

Probably because of [feature staging](https://github.com/rust-lang/rfcs/blob/master/text/0507-release-channels.md#feature-staging).

Example:

``` rust
extern crate test;

pub fn add_two(a: i32) -> i32 {
    a + 2
}

#[cfg(test)]
mod tests {
    use super::*;
    use test::Bencher;

    #[test]
    fn it_works() {
        assert_eq!(4, add_two(2));
    }

    #[bench]
    fn bench_add_two(b: &mut Bencher) {
        b.iter(|| add_two(2));
    }
}
```

